'''Ddin''' neɣ '''asɣan''' d tagrawt n [[tikti|tektiwin]] d tifelsin id yesskanayen iswi n [[tudert]] d [[tallunt]] ɣer wid yettamnen yis, Akken yettwasen tikwal d Taflest yettwaqqnen ar [[tadfersengamt|tedfersengamt]] d [[tisunayin]], Akken yeqqen daɣen d [[tafada|tɣara]]

== [[Tudayt]] ==
[[Tudayt]] d asɣan amezwaru ideg ttamnen medden d akken yella yiwen n [[yillu|yellu]] kan. Isem-is s [[tɛebrit|Thibrut]] ''Yehweh'', [[Udayen]] ur zmiren ara ad bedren isem agi acku ɣur-sen d amuggi (leḥram). Yellu g tudayt ila (yesɛa) iylan i t-yettallen, yuzen [[amazun]] ɣur [[afgan|ifganen]] i wakken ad ttamnen yyis

== [[Tamasiḥit]] ==
G [[Tamasiḥit|trumit]] [[yillu|yellu]] d amesnalfu yuderen ɣer medden s iman n wedmaw umi ssentayen [[Ɛisa|yissu]].

== [[Islam|Tineslemt]] ==
G [[islam|tneslemt]], Yellu d yiwen maca ur yudir ara, [[Muḥemmed]] d [[amazun]] aneggar yakk ara ad yazen yellu ar ifganen, i wakken ad t-defren yakk s umgarad n tgurmiwin-nsen d initen n sen d [[tutlayt|tutlayin-nsen]] 


